    "title": "The legend lives.",
    "description": "Fires a two-shot burst per trigger pull with a long pause between bursts, and adds extra pellets on top of the normal shotgun blast."
  },
  "notes": "Each trigger pull fires a two-shot burst, and each shot consumes 2 ammo, so every burst uses 4 shells. Fire-rate bonuses also shorten the delay between bursts, and even modest boosts are noticeable. It uses a Jakobs double barrel rather than a Bandit barrel. It can roll different accessories, but the prefix is not shown in the name. A hotfix on October 14, 2013 increased Bandit shotgun magazine size by 1 and slightly improved reload speed.",
